<p>HBC will be offering free broadband Internet. This service is available to our area. Please contact HBC if you are in need of an Internet connection during the time of the school closure. With area schools amending class schedules in response to the coronavirus, HBC will be offering free broadband Internet to eligible low-income families with students. <a data-ft='{"tn":"-U"}' data-lynx-mode="async" data-lynx-uri="https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fow.ly%2FIWjI50yLTTM%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1f0rK5ivuibb13TsVhh2yX8Sd9_oqkDJ6plWha332UMPlceRqqmZ-K-YI&amp;h=AT2_3SxUDqm037avokZqamoaQtxT2SELGjx8aOF1dZUMCwhS0klEtxUk1212gGTze5RonbGpB-sKclV4hiu8NSEAnvJOH5yD7aC1znVpMvOceXibOKYuyO87NjznRHuuzB9BVxvkuVg0bSvlZOofqDXoGBYKz9u_IlIEj9gGapgNx1iCCSLVi7mB8MSwx7EFu-XjoKwwBW5Y7JBZ1sbTDROP6wapAkBCnQdG8yPmbh4GxzEEeuxoeuxNwIJPJx8v3T8N8dlGJBe1p7HYJxq_Zu58s_uCAyyAOObSblp7sm7tkxxoA-9Bww0nplKbVRdBS7YxWDhN1zGw_dSGUdLh2UHUqoxNjri466voPYeLYNIPwz5H9tMlsMy2fVcESjI9ajooff_arBBYKGjOnm5pfB1N_Hc4L5oxDTEKmtRn7XrexKkghlLFaEyLfBWSnxyIsqgprcuw7li4Jo8nu-A7Vz7yjWWaf0noZL9tDYwoKoiLqguOT3fph-bxDYP9lWNxtCMlQpNNiwGr8eJ1LsDtcUl2n78BhOKuuALmQpSUImV--knJ-uBZ5NwxRSC8cK6Cz5TsaKNc3qPGpuGcQH6E3N2mjbvNjT3SvPHAfJk8IwJz3pE2N7dFepwdIFZLRj7itiwFjoVtCjuCFisFXkNpbk4j3rORgMFKiLElvP1Xgq1sc3zHgbAp19AnrQ5XM9CrAs2Jqz2MPUTVTUywJWoBmG3QrrCUVejUajTH45NB9IqMGo5xS-BuxFAFNFTSaD_ESRjJM0nJEHVLWxvczged20Oq_kPSmK1q1sc78yW4eicB3E_zEKRhIkXwiEuXznyKFh-SFhGuk8bjYjeVmJjf5A" href="http://ow.ly/IWjI50yLTTM?fbclid=IwAR1f0rK5ivuibb13TsVhh2yX8Sd9_oqkDJ6plWha332UMPlceRqqmZ-K-YI" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">http://ow.ly/IWjI50yLTTM</a></p>
